price: Beekaan waan fagoofi dhihoo sun (qulqullaa’e), Waan isaan itti dabalan irraa ol ta’e!
arabic: عَٰلِمِ ٱلۡغَيۡبِ وَٱلشَّهَٰدَةِ فَتَعَٰلَىٰ عَمَّا يُشۡرِكُونَ

version.title: Oromo translation
version.description: Translation of the Quran meanings into Oromo by Ghaly Ababour Abaghuna, printed in 2009.

meta.transliteration: ʿālimi al-ghaybi wal-shahādati fataʿālā ʿammā yush'rikūna
